nodes.text: Waks Trode was a male Ishi Tib who was the owner of an industrial company and was the Associate Planetary Representative of Tibrin. He served alongside his fellow Ishi Tib Senator, Gume Saam. He profited from the Clone Wars. In 19 BBY, he attended the production of Squid Lake at the Galaxies Opera House, trying to charm Senators into giving him contracts.
